The paper deals with image-based virtual try-on, which involves generating a photo-realistic image of a person wearing a desired clothing item. This task falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The paper also uses machine learning techniques, specifically generative models, to achieve its goal, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses image processing techniques to refine the synthesized image, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
